    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >展开一段充满挑战的旅程，扮演一个金色弹跳的神器，唯一的目标是到达一座古老神秘塔的顶端。但要小心，这座塔有自己的意志，会不择手段地操纵您放弃您的任务。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >1000米的挑战</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >攀登一座高达一公里的塔，塔内充满了致命的障碍，每个都比前一个更致命。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=326 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/dfd51de96f10d0653daea272e0f51889.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >易于上手，难以精通</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过简单直观的物理控制，准备好接受技能和精确度的真正考验，挑战越来越艰难的关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/f0a4da36a9424e0b9bcc467517d20708.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >有灵系统</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在这段意想不到的旅程中，与一座有灵塔互动，她会通过显示在墙上的大量句子与您交流。拥有超过1000句反映讽刺、绝望、愤怒、无聊等情绪的独特句子，您将一边努力克服塔的巨大挑战，一边忍受她不断的挑衅，展开一场智慧和意志的战斗。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.poster.avif?t=1757324108\" width=600 height=336 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.webm?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3102100/extras/492a8e1265d8a776c7a9eb1f88f5848b.mp4?t=1757324108\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于那些决定购买游戏的人，非常感谢，这对我意义重大！！！记住：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >愿您的攀登迅速，决心坚定！</p>",
